					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Sprite coordinates aren't negative, so sprites at Y=255 are not at Y=-1, they are out of range, so they are never evaluated.<br /><br />Also, it looks like at around scanline 138, it stops scrolling correctly in both games.  Hope you don't have any bad for loops that are stopping too early.<br /><br />How about the full list of 2000 and 2005/2006 writes that happen during a particular frame, and the timestamp (scanline and dot number) that each write occurs at?  If there are any writes that aren't supposed to exist, that would suggest a CPU problem.  If the writes match other emulators, then it's a PPU emulation problem.</div>

					
